717832f-b.text:
(1) Broadway west side, between 220 and 221 Streets, looking south, has since disappeared from 1929.

(2) North side Broadway between 22O and 221 Streets looking north, disappeared since 1929.

(3) Barns of house toward Bovee field, west from Broadway, later was Park Tenod west on Seaver Avenue, Isac Micheal Dyekan.

(4) West side of Broadway at 217th Street, Gate Lodge of Seaman House.

E. P. Chrystie.

Ju1y 1, 1923.
